title: Chilling Adventures of Sabrina Episode 6 "An Exorcism in Greendale" Breakdown!
author: Think Story
comment: You’re the only person I can find whose making legit breakdown videos of this show. I gotta subscribe now haha
When I saw Susie in the dress I thought she was wearing it as a sign of support for Uncle Jesse, but based on the conversation she had with Sabrina what you mentioned makes more sense.
i have to say, your inserts in every breakdown have me cracking tf up. great break downs! helps me understand what i've missed!
You said Sabrina didn't believe her friends despite having just fought a demon. This isn't correct, it's clear she was feigning disbelief because her friends can't know about her world.
